photoswipe markup
Root element of PhotoSwipe. Must have class pswp.
Background of PhotoSwipe. 
         It's a separate element as animating opacity is faster than rgba().
Slides wrapper with overflow:hidden.
Container that holds slides. 
            PhotoSwipe keeps only 3 of them in the DOM to save memory.
            Don't modify these 3 pswp__item elements, data is added later on.
Default (PhotoSwipeUI_Default) interface on top of sliding area. Can be changed.
Controls are self-explanatory. Order can be changed.

About
About Us
Oaklodge Mobile Home Park is a family park located close to the Naval Air Station in Pensacola, Florida. World class beaches are within miles of the entrance to Oaklodge. We have one lot rental left for a home or a recreational vehicle. We have homes for sale and rent. Why rent an apartment when you can rent or buy a home? On site professional management, On site professional maintenance, Paved streets, Street lights, Great neighbors, Off street parking, Guest parking, Locked mailboxes, Attractive wooded home sites, City water and sewer, School bus stops within the community and more!!!!
Contact Oaklodge Manufactured Home Community
to rent or buy a
manufactured home
in beautiful, sunny
Pensacola, Florida
.
